# Redirect rules, grouped by product.
# Netlify evaluates rules top to bottom, first match wins, and non-forced
# redirects never fire for paths that exist as real pages. Netlify doesn't
# chain redirects within a request, so within each product the specific page
# rules MUST come before any wildcard or version-strip rules that would
# otherwise shadow them.

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Changelog
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Tag shortcuts
/changelog/seqera-cloud        /changelog/tags/seqera-cloud        301
/changelog/seqera-enterprise   /changelog/tags/seqera-enterprise   301

